{"tid":1456200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心啊！！！狗記招今日好撚鬼","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:15.000Z","uid":238346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7d00b7ba9898555dac9fe2a5d2638857f50123","tid":1456200,"uid":238346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"我番工無野做就睇記招<br />\n睇下班傻鳩點比記者屌<br />\n<br />\n但係每一日嘅共通點就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">５點即走</span></strong>！<br />\n甚至係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未夠５點就走</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日搵幾條撚樣出嚟講咁撚耐<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留曬啲senior記者係記者會</span></strong><br />\n係咪想shift focus 等人唔好留意機場？<br />\n<br />\n係咪機場會有咩大事發生？<br />\n我真係唔想有手足再比人拉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>走啊　好撚奇怪啊真係</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e24fccd581f8b6f3cac2add7646df0faf3f8f3","tid":1456200,"uid":294498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:52:38.000Z","msg":"最少宜家已經傳到咁勁，居然都冇其他台開LIVE<br />\n實有問題"},{"pid":"1550bc530709d8e5aea81c4338c6a74bf6985738","tid":1456200,"uid":238346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9157762f02b4356b7063ad0988c96dcb10707b00","tid":1456200,"uid":238346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e24fccd581f8b6f3cac2add7646df0faf3f8f3","tid":1456200,"uid":294498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:52:38.000Z","msg":"最少宜家已經傳到咁勁，居然都冇其他台開LIVE<br />\n實有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"我想搵嗰時好似冇大台去報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26